{"tid":1576131,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Be water- 企係道德高地運用武力","createTime":"2019-09-17T06:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:42:31.000Z","uid":49898,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5370569a74033311d23ffacae2346d33752d509a","tid":1576131,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"一直幫助我哋嘅twitter 用戶Enzo Mazak警示左我地嘅危機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1575216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1575216</a><br />\n<br />\n頭先睇左依個post，想針對佢列果幾個point講講我睇法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 反擊（武力上）</span></span><br />\n我之前都開過post講破窗效應<br />\n任由對手無底線咁打我地斬我地係等死<br />\n係和平理性道理法律都阻止唔到對手嘅情況下<br />\n令對手（仆親）係必須<br />\n而且要快狠準 最好唔好俾人影到<br />\n達到阻嚇作用就夠<br />\n唔駛日日清算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只可以反擊</span></span><br />\n一定唔可以主動攻擊<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span></span><br />\n唔係就好易俾人感覺好似對家果啲恐佈份子<br />\n咁樣會令我地無左光環<br />\n悟空平時都愛好和平啦<br />\n係無限俾人打先變超西姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要外國幫手就要用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">道德感召</span></span><br />\n特別係宜家人權法仲係議會傾緊<br />\n所以非必要都唔好暴力<br />\n除非最後外國都唔幫我地先要絕地反擊<br />\n<br />\n總之而家要做嘅係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄉黑/ 大6狗</span></span> 打+文宣解釋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑狗</span></span> 救人+打（睇環境，對家裝備）+文宣解釋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. blackbloc vs 街坊裝</span></span><br />\n勇武先blackbloc<br />\n和理非就街坊裝<br />\n依樣我無乜意見<br />\n但想自保就真勇武場合先戰鬥格好啲<br />\n和理非場合俾狗周到真係死得唔抵（only黑衫都夠死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 目的論</span></span><br />\n每次行動嘅目的係好緊要<br />\n明顯宜家運動個初心俾對手轉到有啲亂<br />\n我地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做野前更加要問why what how</span></span><br />\n我知道有啲搞手好不負責任（係話你呀 望）<br />\n宜家搞活動係真係會有傷亡<br />\n要認真諗清楚可行性 唔好推手足去死<br />\n<br />\n任務達成就走人 千祈唔好戀戰<br />\n前線 中間和理非係進退要溝通 （多左旗手同企中前嘅和理非 好似好左）<br />\n唔好又估估下 最後又拖到對家擺曬陣黎清場<br />\n最後最重要嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每個人自己一定要定好撤走方式先好出發</span></span><br />\n真係可以救你一命"},{"pid":"172855a016f5ebcd0c153ea19da1a6cf46744c0d","tid":1576131,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"df3975f4f27638494a3465b5f95eced59ce7b99d","tid":1576131,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ce3a4a33729059e1648a8147c81f5c468dc9cc1","tid":1576131,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1070f1443235088f3e29ff791dbe591d4eaa314","tid":1576131,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b390710afe30ec1fa25aab47ca775e2ef336cc3","tid":1576131,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ed8569e0398debbc24d345c8cd182df6a41c4d8","tid":1576131,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAABnFb.png\" data-t